Search for:UCR's Academic Personnel eFile system represents a significant improvement of the academic personnel review process for faculty. Assembling and reviewing faculty merit and promotion portfolios will be faster, simpler and more efficient using this stable, secure, flexible system. Updated, accurate, and comprehensible information is essential to the faculty review process, and this is exactly what eFile can provide. We plan to add all academic personnel to this system over the next few years.To login to the eFile system, visit https://efile.ucr.edu Note: To login, your department will need to grant access.